        <td>Diminished WH</td>
        <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-mid)"><strong style="color:var(--orange)">Any tempo:</strong> Symmetric — transpose any pattern up 3 frets = same scale. Perfect for fast repeating cells. Often used as passing chord.</td>
        <td style="color:var(--hadrien);font-size:12px">Dim WH cells</td>
        <td style="color:var(--patitucci);font-size:12px">Dim WH</td>
